      "category": "RECAP",
      "date": "Feb 10, 2026",
      "html": "<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7aedfb2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"7aedfb2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"cvGsUA direction-ltr align-start para-style-body\"><span class=\"a_GcMg font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">Join our team and become a Brand Ambassador for the upcoming SX Festival.</span></p>\n<p class=\"cvGsUA direction-ltr align-start para-style-body\"> </p>\n<p class=\"cvGsUA direction-ltr align-start para-style-body\"><span class=\"a_GcMg font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">This is an exclusive program created for a carefully selected group of collaborators from diverse backgrounds including content creators, industry professionals, artists, media personalities, influencers, and other inspiring voices who want to be part of something meaningful and forward thinking.</span></p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ce5a504 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"ce5a504\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-cd8e150 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"cd8e150\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d8bbbf4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"d8bbbf4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"347\" height=\"347\" src=\"https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/ph2.webp\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-770\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/ph2.webp 347w, https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/ph2-300x300-1.webp 300w, https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/ph2-150x150-1.webp 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 347px) 100vw, 347px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8390a6f e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"8390a6f\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e490f10 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"e490f10\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"347\" height=\"347\" src=\"https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/ph2-2.webp\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-771\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/ph2-2.webp 347w, https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/ph2-2-300x300-1.webp 300w, https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/ph2-2-150x150-1.webp 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 347px) 100vw, 347px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a3741cc e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"a3741cc\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3691735 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"3691735\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"347\" height=\"347\" src=\"https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/ph4.webp\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-772\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/ph4.webp 347w, https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/ph4-300x300-1.webp 300w, https://sx.zds.es/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/ph4-150x150-1.webp 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 347px) 100vw, 347px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-620380d e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"620380d\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9bede12 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"9bede12\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"cvGsUA direction-ltr align-start para-style-body\"><span class=\"a_GcMg font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">We want to grow together with you and share this journey as partners. As a Brand Ambassador, you will receive a starter package with a value of 800 EUR in goods and VIP entries. You will also have the opportunity to monetize through ticket sales and enjoy priority access to VIP seats before anyone else.</span></p>\n<p class=\"cvGsUA direction-ltr align-start para-style-body\"><span class=\"a_GcMg font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">If this resonates with you, apply by completing the </span><a class=\"a_GcMg font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-underline text-strikethrough-none\" draggable=\"false\" href=\"https://wkf.ms/49zQjCt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">application form.</a></p>\n<p class=\"cvGsUA direction-ltr align-start para-style-body\"><span class=\"a_GcMg font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">Our team will review all submissions and get back to you within seven working days from the moment we receive your application. If selected, we will personally contact you and guide you through the onboarding process.</span></p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-652f7c1 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"652f7c1\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-44b971d elementor-mobile-align-justify elementor-widget-mobile__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"44b971d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm\" href=\"#\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">join our<br />newsletter</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-804a87c elementor-mobile-align-justify elementor-widget-mobile__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"804a87c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm\" href=\"#\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">BECOME A SPONSOR</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>"
